title: Metallic Reactance
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The metals in your armor are carefully alloyed to ground electricity and protect from acidic chemical reactions. 

You gain resistance equal to 3 + half your level to <<tag Acid>> and <<tag Electricity>> damage. When under the effects of [[Overdrive]], the resistance increases by 2.